Cook rice as directed on package, omitting salt. Meanwhile, stir-fry chicken in half the Simmer Sauce in large skillet until done. Add vegetables and remaining Simmer Sauce to skillet; cook and stir 2 to 4 min. or until vegetables are crisp-tender. Stir in Finishing Sauce and pineapple; stir-fry 1 to 2 min. or until heated through. Serve over rice.